**Coin template** `<span class="coin"></span>`

<span class="coin"></span>
<style>
  .coin {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    right: 10px;

    background-color: #ddd;
    color: #444;

    border: 2px solid currentColor;
    border-radius: 50%;

    font-weight: bold;

    width: 2em;
    height: 2em;
  }

  .coin::before {
    content: '.';
    display: block;
  }
</style>

