**Coin purse (6)** `<div class="purse"></div>`

<div class="purse">
  <span class="coin"></span>
  <span class="coin"></span>
  <span class="coin"></span>
</div>

<style>
  .purse {
    height: 0;
    width: 0;
  }

  .purse .coin {
    transform: translateY(0);
    z-index: 6;
  }

  .purse .coin
       ~ .coin {
    transform: translateY(10px);
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .purse .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin {
    transform: translateY(20px);
    z-index: 4;
  }

  .purse .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin {
    transform: translateY(30px);
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .purse .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin {
    transform: translateY(40px);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .purse .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin
       ~ .coin {
    transform: translateY(50px);
    z-index: 1;
  }
</style>

**Section** `<div class="section">Section</div>`

<div class="section">Section</div>

With a short description

<style>
  .section {
    background-color: rgba(251, 236, 191, 0.84);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .section::before,
  .section::after {
    content: 'üëá';
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    color: #884321;
  }

  .section::before {

    margin-right: 1em;
  }

  .section::after {
    transform: scaleX(-1);
    margin-left: 1em;
  }

  .section + p {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 1em;
  }
</style>

**Captioned blockquote** `<blockquote title="Title" cite="www.example.com">Blockquote text</blockquote>`

<blockquote title="Title" cite="www.example.com">Blockquote text with both `title` and `cite`</blockquote>

<blockquote cite="www.example.com/really/long/url/to/show/that/text/will/be/truncated">Blockquote text with just `cite`</blockquote>

<blockquote title="Title">Blockquote text with just `title`</blockquote>

<style>
  blockquote[title]::after,
  blockquote[cite]::after,
  blockquote[title][cite]::after {
    display: list-item;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    font-style: italic;
    list-style-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1em 1em" width="0.6em" height="1em"><text x="0" y="1em">‚Äî</text></svg>');
    padding-left: 1em;
    margin-left: -1em;
    list-style-position: inside;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    text-indent: -1em;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: pre;
  }

  blockquote[title]::after {
    content: attr(title);
  }

  blockquote[cite]::after {
    content: attr(cite);
  }

  blockquote[cite][title]::after {
    content: attr(title)'\a'attr(cite);
  }
</style>
